acl: group: Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-acl --group --name NAME --path PATH [OPTIONS...]

Group control:

Group options:
  -n [ --name ] arg      Group name
  -c [ --create ]        Create the group
  --description arg      Description of group
  --show                 List group users, administrators and description
  --add-user arg         Add user to group
  --add-admin arg        Add administrator to group
  --add-group arg        Add group to group
  --add arg              Add users, administrators and groups to group (prefix:
                         @<group>, ^<admin>)
  --remove-user arg      Remove user from group
  --remove-admin arg     Remove administrator from group
  --remove-group arg     Remove group from group
  --remove arg           Remove users, administrators and groups from group 
                         (prefix: @<group>, ^<admin>)
  -p [ --path ] arg      A path within the volume
  --verbose              Verbose output
  --fetch                Fetch users from the Hub if needed

Hidden options:
  --fallback-xattrs      Fallback to alternate xattr mode if system xattrs are 
                         not suppported


